Finally, the <a data-link-type="dfn" href="https://www.w3.org/TR/css-grid-2/#grid-container" id="ref-for-grid-container①⓪⑥">grid container</a> is sized
			using the resulting size of the <a data-link-type="dfn" href="https://www.w3.org/TR/css-grid-2/#grid" id="ref-for-grid②⑧">grid</a> as its content size,
			and the tracks are aligned within the <span id="ref-for-grid-container①⓪⑦">grid container</span> according to the <a class="property" data-link-type="propdesc" href="https://www.w3.org/TR/css-align-3/#propdef-align-content" id="ref-for-propdef-align-content①⓪">align-content</a> and <a class="property" data-link-type="propdesc" href="https://www.w3.org/TR/css-align-3/#propdef-justify-content" id="ref-for-propdef-justify-content①⓪">justify-content</a> properties.
